k, SMTP/API delivery, mailbox receipt), which in-process fakes can mask. MOCK-HIDE: mocked email client can hide auth, routing, MIME, or deliverability failures. LLM-DEP: behavior text targets end-to-end delivery to inbox, not quality of model decisions. MULTI-STEP: not defined as multiple agentic decisions to validate. REJECTION-GATE: Agentic rejected because the disqualifying text is `reaches ... inbox correctly`; acceptance criterion is transport success, not summary semantic quality.","test_description":"Execute end-to-end run against real/staging data endpoints and real email delivery service to a test mailbox; verify received message, recipients, subject/body presence, and expected report sections from all stages.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.0,"Integration":0.08,"System":0.78,"Agentic":0.12,"Workflow":0.02}},{"behavior_id":5,"description":"When the email delivery service is unreachable, the generated report is saved to a local file and delivery is retried on the next scheduled run.","minimum_level":"System","justification":"REAL-INFRA: failure involves real delivery-service unreachability plus filesystem persistence across runs; OS/network/subprocess timing/state can cause failures hidden by pure mocks. MOCK-HIDE: faking delivery and storage can miss real connection-error classes, file write/permissions, and re-run pickup behavior. LLM-DEP: correctness is retry/persistence mechanics, not model output quality. MULTI-STEP: sequential runs are needed, but not multiple agentic decisions. REJECTION-GATE: Integration rejected because behavior text includes `service is unreachable` and `saved to a local file ... retried on the next scheduled run`, which crosses real infra boundaries.","test_description":"With real filesystem and scheduler invocation path, force delivery endpoint to be unreachable (e.g., blocked/staging outage), confirm report is persisted to fallback file, then run next schedule cycle with service restored and verify queued report is sent and local fallback is cleared/marked delivered.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.0,"Integration":0.14,"System":0.8,"Agentic":0.04,"Workflow":0.02}}]}
